    "본문HTML": "<p>\n\n</p><p class=\"HStyle0\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 17.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 바탕;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 굴림체; line-height: 20.8px;\">서울미래인재재단은 2026년 &lt;서울인재해외교환학생장학금&gt; 장학생을 다음과 같이 선발합니다.</span></p>\n<div id=\"hwpEditorBoardContent\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"> </div>\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"> </div>\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\n<p class=\"HStyle0\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 17.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 바탕;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 굴림체; color: rgb(0, 0, 255); line-height: 20.8px;\">가. 장학금명: </span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 굴림체; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 0, 255); line-height: 20.8px;\">서울인재해외교환학생장학금</span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle0\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 17.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 바탕;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 굴림체; line-height: 20.8px;\">나. 지원자격:</span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle0\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 17.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 바탕;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 굴림체; line-height: 20.8px;\">- 서울 소재 4년제 대학·전문대학·전공대학의 정규학기 학부생(휴학생 포함)으로</span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle0\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 17.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 바탕;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 굴림체; line-height: 20.8px;\">2026년 2학기 해외 교환·방문학생 파견(예정) 학생</span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle0\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; li